OL,3,CTake a tour of the the new 'Aurora'
OL,4,Ctrain to run on the Midland Mainline
OL,6,FRajiv Popat explored one of the new
OL,7,F'Aurora' trains and its new features.
OL,9,FA new #400 million fleet of partly
OL,10,Felectric trains has been unveiled to
OL,11,Frun across the Midland Mainline.
OL,13,FThe line is electrified only from
OL,14,FLondon to Hinckley in Leicestershire;
OL,15,Fbeyond that, trains are powered by
OL,16,Fless environmentally friendly diesel -
OL,17,Fso these trains will switch between
OL,18,Fthe two power sources.
