OL,3,CTake a tour of the the new 'Aurora'
OL,4,Ctrain to run on the Midland Mainline
OL,6,FDespite that, East Midlands Railway
OL,7,Fsays the 33 'Aurora' trains will
OL,8,F"revolutionise" rail travel along the
OL,9,FMidland Mainline and reduce their
OL,10,Fcarbon footprint.
OL,12,FWill Rodgers, the managing director,
OL,13,Fsays that the trains will produce "66%
OL,14,Fless carbon from London to Sheffield."
OL,15,FHe argued that not continuing the
OL,16,Felectrification was one of the "tough
OL,17,Fchoices" necessary for these
OL,18,Finfrastructure projects.
