OL,4,Ctrain to run on the Midland Mainline
OL,6,FEast Midlands Railway said it would
OL,7,Fcost #1.5 billion to electrify the
OL,8,Fline fully.
OL,10,FThe Labour MP for Derby South, Baggy
OL,11,FShankar, said that the full
OL,12,Felectrification isn't "affordable",
OL,13,Fbut when that changes, he will push
OL,14,Ffor it.
OL,16,FThe new trains to run on the line will
OL,17,Fhave seats designed in Derby and a
OL,18,Fbetter mobile signal, thanks to
OL,19,Fspecially designed glass. The first
OL,20,Ftrain from the fleet will run on the
OL,21,Fline in December.
