OL,3,CTake a tour of the the new 'Aurora'
OL,4,Ctrain to run on the Midland Mainline
OL,6,FDerby-based design firm DG DESIGN
OL,7,Fworked on the new seat aiming for more
OL,8,Fcomfort and support. They also have
OL,9,Fpower and USB points, generous
OL,10,Flegroom, coat hooks, well-sized seat-
OL,11,Fback tables for all seats and space to
OL,12,Fstow a cabin-bag under each seat.
OL,14,FIn a statement, Will Rogers added:
OL,15,F"The introduction of our first Aurora
OL,16,Ftrain this December marks the start of
OL,17,Fa new era for Intercity travel across
OL,18,Fthe East Midlands and South Yorkshire.
