OL,6,F"Our Auroras have been designed with
OL,7,Four customers at their heart; with
OL,8,Fmore seats, greater comfort, better
OL,9,Fconnectivity and a smoother, quieter
OL,10,Fride.
OL,12,F"We and our colleagues at Transport UK
OL,13,Fare delighted to be delivering a
OL,14,Frailway that our customers,
OL,15,Fcommunities and our employees can
OL,16,Ftruly take pride in."
