OL,6,FA DfT spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fcommitted to electrifying and
OL,8,Fdecarbonising our railway, but we need
OL,9,Fto do this in the most cost-effective
OL,10,Fway and focus on schemes that make the
OL,11,Fgreatest difference as quickly as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,F"Although further electrification of
OL,15,Fthe Midland Main Line to Sheffield has
OL,16,Fbeen paused, we will continue to keep
OL,17,Fthe scheme under review for when
OL,18,Ffurther funding becomes available."
